
  MCP Server Ideas

  1. System & Hardware MCP

  - Get CPU/RAM/disk usage
  - List running processes, kill processes
  - Monitor network interfaces and connections
  - Read/write environment variables
  - Execute system commands with sandboxing
  - Hardware info (battery, display, etc.)

  2. Database MCP

  - Connect to SQLite, PostgreSQL, MySQL
  - Execute queries, list tables
  - Schema inspection and ERD generation
  - Data export (CSV, JSON)
  - Query builder and ORM-like operations

  3. File System MCP

  - Advanced file operations (compress, extract, convert)
  - Watch directories for changes
  - File type detection and metadata extraction
  - Batch rename, find duplicates
  - File permission management

  4. Git/Version Control MCP

  - Advanced git operations (rebase, cherry-pick, bisect)
  - Branch visualization and comparison
  - Conflict detection and merge assistance
  - Repository analytics (contributor stats, commit history)
  - Multi-repo management

  5. API Testing MCP

  - Send HTTP requests (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE)
  - GraphQL query execution
  - WebSocket connections
  - Request/response logging
  - API documentation parsing (OpenAPI/Swagger)

  6. Image Processing MCP

  - Resize, crop, rotate images
  - Apply filters (blur, sharpen, contrast)
  - Format conversion (PNG, JPEG, WebP)
  - OCR text extraction
  - Image comparison and diffing

  7. PDF Operations MCP

  - Extract text/images from PDFs
  - Merge/split PDF files
  - Add watermarks, page numbers
  - Fill PDF forms
  - Convert to/from PDF

  8. Email MCP

  - Send emails via SMTP
  - Read emails via IMAP
  - Email parsing and attachment handling
  - Email template rendering
  - Bulk email operations

  9. Media Processing MCP

  - Audio/video transcoding (ffmpeg wrapper)
  - Extract audio from video
  - Trim, merge, concatenate media
  - Extract metadata
  - Generate thumbnails

  10. Docker MCP

  - List/start/stop containers
  - Build images
  - View logs and exec into containers
  - Compose operations
  - Container health monitoring

  11. Kubernetes MCP

  - List pods, deployments, services
  - Apply manifests
  - Port forwarding
  - Log streaming
  - Resource scaling

  12. Cloud Storage MCP

  - AWS S3, Google Cloud Storage, Azure Blob
  - Upload/download files
  - Generate presigned URLs
  - Bucket management
  - Cross-cloud transfers

  13. Calendar/Scheduling MCP

  - Read/write Google Calendar, Outlook
  - Create events and reminders
  - Find free time slots
  - Timezone conversions
  - Recurring event management

  14. Notification MCP

  - Send push notifications
  - Slack/Discord/Telegram messages
  - SMS via Twilio
  - Desktop notifications
  - Webhook triggers

  15. AI/ML Operations MCP

  - Run local LLM inference (llama.cpp, Ollama)
  - Image classification
  - Text embeddings and vector search
  - Whisper transcription
  - Image generation (Stable Diffusion)

  16. Cryptocurrency MCP

  - Get prices and market data
  - Check wallet balances
  - Transaction history
  - DeFi protocol interactions
  - NFT metadata lookup

  17. Package Manager MCP

  - npm, pip, cargo operations
  - Dependency analysis
  - Vulnerability scanning
  - Version management
  - Lockfile updates

  18. Testing Framework MCP

  - Run unit tests (pytest, jest)
  - Code coverage reporting
  - Test discovery
  - Mocking and fixtures
  - CI integration

  19. Spreadsheet MCP

  - Read/write Excel, CSV, Google Sheets
  - Data manipulation (sort, filter, pivot)
  - Formula evaluation
  - Chart generation
  - Data validation

  20. Social Media MCP

  - Post to Twitter/X, Instagram, LinkedIn
  - Fetch feeds and mentions
  - Analytics and engagement data
  - Comment/reply automation
  - Hashtag research

